articles.title: Dublin's Ubotica reveals latest platform to send AI into space - SiliconRepublic.com
articles.description: Ubotica said its new platform is compatible with various satellites including miniature cubesats, letting them perform AI-based applications.
articles.content:
Ubotica said its new hardware platform is designed to be compatible with miniature cube satellites and will expand the capabilities of Earth observation systems.
